data.description: This document contains use cases and requirements for the OMA Presence SIMPLE Data Extensions (PDE) Enabler, taking into consideration the demands of end-users, service providers, and system implementers. The PDE describes Presence Information Elements for the OMA Presence SIMPLE Enabler.

The scope of this document is limited to the Reference Release Definition of the Presence SIMPLE Data Extensions (PDE) version 1.0 according to OMA Release process and the Reference Release document baseline listed in section 5.
